page.title: 19POPULATION OF ASHLEY GREEN
page.content: Ashley Green population is at present 523. 261 males and 262 females. 271 people are married, comprising, 136 males and 135 females. There are 199 single people, comprising 114 males and 85 females. There are 27 students, 17 being male and 10 females. Of the 75 plus range, there are 10 males and 13 females, compared with up to four years, 13 males and 12 females. There are a total of 529 residents in Ashley Green. 492 being of British national- ity, and 476 being English. At present 529 being female. There are 30 people mostly aged between 25-44 that are relative newcomers to Ashley Green in the last couple of years. There are only 21 retired males, the oldest residents being 4 ladies aged 85 plus.
